DISCORD_CHANNEL_ID: <single int or int array [xxx, xxx] where the source of images are uploaded to> (remove the <> and quotes, for multiple channels, replace xxx with channel ids)
DESTINATION_DISCORD_CHANNEL_ID: <int where embed for starboard will be sent> (remove the <> and quotes)
UNIQUE_USERS_THRESHOLD: <int> how many unique users need to react to the message to be sent to the starboard> (remove the <> and quotes)
DELAY_TIME: <int> how long to wait before checking for new messages> (remove the <> and quotes)
